{
  "texts": [
    "Besides, U-Net plays an important role in segmenting while preserving the information for spatial location with its encoder-decoder structure and skip connections, thus allowing high-value localization of cancerous areas.",
    "This combination of the technique will, therefore, provide the framework with the best performance concerning the classification and segmentation tasks while gaining a good clinical application.",
    "A high performance on the major classes, as confirmed by the confusion matrix and ROC curves, speaks to its capability of handling diverse datasets effectively, hence guaranteeing consistent and reliable results.",
    "Although the overall performance for the PolyNet-DWT-CADx framework was very good, there were some classes that presented some challenges in detection and segmentation.",
    "The confusion matrix underlines several classes, such as Class 7 and Class 8, where misclassifications occurred due to the overlapping features and limited sample diversity."
  ]
}